div.div:
- Focus on goals
- Use reward/punishment for motivation
- Reactive in nature
- Idiosyncracy:
- Space to be creative and inventive
- Initially conforming to group norms
- Group feels they have elected their leader
- Ensuring leaders are considered competent to fulfill group objectives.
- Leaders identify with group, it's ideals and aspirations
- Leader is representative/prototypical of group.
